public class EpicServiceApplicationInterfaceImplementation
extends org.mobilesynergies.android.epic.service.interfaces.IEpicServiceApplicationInterface.Stub

Implementation of the EpicServiceApplicationInterface. All functions run in the thread of the caller and block it. Therefore the functions will call handlers in the EpicService thread.
